[x] Dev and Test builds should offer the user a Tests Panel, which should be hidden in the Production build. 

[x] The tests panel would provide the user with the ability to validate claims and manually perform some tests.

[x] There shall be a Testing panel after the community panel, with a list of UI changes to test.  Maintain the Testing with appropriate changes, and remove untested items that are no longer relevant due to more recent changes.

The Dev/Test user can check-off the items they have tested manually, and this will be remembered.

